---
source: tools/lxperm/tests/integration.rs
expression: out.to_plain()
---
config.txt  [-rw-r--r--]  risk: standard
  Owner can read and write; group and others can only read. Standard read-only sharing.

script.sh  [-rwxrwxrwx]  risk: warning
  All users can read, write, and execute. Anyone can modify this script.

uploads  [drwxrwxrwx]  risk: critical
  World-writable directory. Any user can create or delete files here.
